Lin Chi-ling (1974.11.29) tatayna, nalecuhan i Taywan Taypak. u singanganay a model, tatayna palaway atu telunay. napahezek i Canada Tolunto tabakiay a cacudadan, minanam tu kulitay atu kyizay. singangan tu ci Lin Chiling i 2004 a mihcan, matineng tu ku binawlan cinizaan. 2008 a mihcan, mipalaw iga "sumanahay cabeng", 2010 a mihcan mipalaw nu Lipunay a iga "mamidang nu bulad".
